Business Brief -- Microdyne Corp.:
   Chairman Lowers His Stake
   In the Company to 65.9%
Mr. Cunningham had filed with the SEC stating his
intention to sell 400,000 shares of the company's common
stock. According to the filing, Mr. Cunningham has sold
210,000 shares and has decided against further sales of
shares.
   Microdyne is an Alexandria, Va., satellite-television
equipment concern.